del S 和 Model X 其实打不了什么价格战，因为它的成本在那，但 Mode3 和 ModelY 是个光板车，本身就是成本很低的车。」李斌指出，在这种情况下，随着比亚迪等中国同行的崛起，特斯拉的价格战也是不得已而为之，恰恰证明了中国品牌做得好。 「它在美国有定价权，因为有百分之六七十的份额，但它在中国只有百分之六七的份额，不到 10%。」李斌表示，蔚来肯定不会跟风降价，因为和特斯拉本就不在一个市场。其指出，作为车企应该思考给用户到底创造了什么价值，用最低的价格去获得最好的产品和服务，经济理论上是不成立的。李斌：蔚来毛利率低参与不了「价格战」，特斯拉在中国不具定价权 - 经济观察网 － 专业财经新闻网站"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-de1ecfede60bb24fd4ff7b8f1a5b112d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "67 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/593457922"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Invj9pJOT84k6EAMaCDk0MTYxMjE1IOyMqaEGMAA4G0AQcgk1OTM0NTc5MjJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1680772101.1725159", "card_id": "Q_593013929", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 54}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "经常跑步的乐趣在哪里？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-894dbff3796fb1bd4e2840abe5983b2c_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "66 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/593013929"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Invj9pJOT84k6EAMaCDk0MDYyNTQ1IJjgmqEGMAE4PUARcgk1OTMwMTM5Mjl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1680772101.1730654", "card_id": "Q_593814050", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 85}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "人需要独处吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-cc50650cce12ebbd8e9c62e04909f293_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "64 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/593814050"}}, "attached_